import { Route, BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Login } from './Login'
import { Registration } from './Registr'
function Home() {
	return (
		<>
			<Router>
				<Route path='/Login' element={<Login />} />
				<Route path='/Registration' element={<Registration />} />
			</Router>
		</>
	)
}

export default Home
